::Feline::

She stopped by a small lake to get a drink.  She had the DNA collector on 
her side, just in case.  She spotted three animals and transformed into 
leopard mode.  She ran and caught two of them.  Grabbing the DNA collector, 
she retrieved the samples as ordered and went back to her bike. "Hmmm, I 
wonder what the commander had in store for these samples. I will have to 
find out when I return. I wonder what advantages I will descover when I 
return." she said purring to herself.  She continued on her way to the 
IronFist.


-Original Message------------
>::Zardus::

>Zardus nods. "Allright. I'll have samples for you shortly. Follow me
>to the lab."
>
>Zardus walks out of the conference room, waiting for Lady Hawk to
>follow. His internal computer silently sends a transmission to
>Feline: "Feline, new orders. Get a fast vehicle and search the planet
>for as many DNA samples as you can find. If you meet anyone, return
>to base immediately."
